text: Denine Latanzo, known mononymously as Denine, is a singer of Freestyle music, in addition to being a songwriter. Denine is best remembered for her song "All Cried Out" (Cover of Lisa Lisa & Cult Jam), which reached # 72 on the Billboard Hot 100. "I Remember You", the singer's second single, reached No. 16 on the Bubbling Under Hot 100 Singles chart (the virtual equivalent to position 116 in the Billboard Hot 100).
